"1 1/2 cups short-grain brown rice","4  dried shiitake mushrooms","1 cup hot water","1/2 cup dried hijiki, wakame, or kombu seaweed","1/2  small onion, finely chopped","1 teaspoon toasted sesame seeds","1 tablespoon dark sesame oil","2 tablespoons low-sodium soy sauce","1 cup shelled edamame","  Toasted sesame seeds (optional)"